divs: Sighting DetailsI witnessed a star like shape pulsating vibrations of the rainbow. It would move around the sky unlike anything I had ever witnessed. It cast down a beam of light which I went under and entered into some sort of vortex. Attached below is the video from Joshua Tree, California on March 30, 2012.
